        <h2>System Design and Analysis: Wind Riders of the Lost River Range(WRLRR) Project</h2>
        <p><strong>Author:</strong> Elvis, <strong>Date Posted:</strong> 05/11/2019</p>

        <p>Through out the semester, we worked in a group for the class INFO 3307: System Analysis and Design, we completed a project that demonstrates system designing concepts. Here, I am posting mostly work that were done by me.</p>
        <p>The project was imaginary and about a company that specializes in outdoor equipments renting and selling. More information in the Introduction section.</p>

